OL,3,CTrump files lawsuit against the BBC
OL,4,Cover Panorama speech edit
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has filed a
OL,7,Fdefamation lawsuit against the BBC for
OL,8,Fselectively editing one of his
OL,9,Fspeeches in an episode of Panorama.
OL,11,FThe BBC said documents filed at a
OL,12,Fcourt in Florida asked for five
OL,13,Fbillion dollars (#3.7 billion) in
OL,14,Fdamages for defamation, as well as the
OL,15,Fsame amount for a claim of violating
OL,16,Ftrade practices.
