OL,3,CTrump files lawsuit against the BBC
OL,4,Cover Panorama speech edit
OL,6,FAccording to the Associated Press, the
OL,7,F33-page lawsuit accuses the
OL,8,Forganisation of broadcasting a "false,
OL,9,Fdefamatory, deceptive, disparaging,
OL,10,Finflammatory, and malicious depiction
OL,11,Fof President Trump", calling it "a
OL,12,Fbrazen attempt to interfere in and
OL,13,Finfluence" the 2024 US presidential
OL,14,Felection.
OL,16,FIt also accused the BBC of "splicing
OL,17,Ftogether two entirely separate parts
OL,18,Fof President Trump's speech on January
OL,19,F6, 2021" in order to "intentionally
OL,20,Fmisrepresent the meaning of what
OL,21,FPresident Trump said".
