OL,3,CTrump files lawsuit against the BBC
OL,4,Cover Panorama speech edit
OL,6,FThe Panorama programme was not shown
OL,7,Fin the US, but the lawsuit says it can
OL,8,Fbe watched on the BritBox subscription
OL,9,Fstreaming platform.
OL,11,FThe BBC said it has not yet responded
OL,12,Fto the filing.
OL,14,FThe scandal unfolded earlier this year
OL,15,Fafter a leaked memo highlighted
OL,16,Fconcerns about the way clips of Mr
OL,17,FTrump's speech on January 6 2021 were
OL,18,Fspliced together so it appeared he had
OL,19,Ftold supporters he was going to walk
OL,20,Fto the US Capitol with them to "fight
OL,21,Flike hell".
