OL,3,CTrump files lawsuit against the BBC
OL,4,Cover Panorama speech edit
OL,6,FMr Trump said the lawsuit was imminent
OL,7,Fwhen he spoke at a press conference on
OL,8,FMonday afternoon in Washington.
OL,10,FHe said: "In a little while, you'll be
OL,11,Fseeing I'm suing the BBC for putting
OL,12,Fwords in my mouth literally. They had
OL,13,Fme saying things that I never said.
OL,15,F"We'll be filing that suit probably
OL,16,Fthis afternoon or tomorrow morning."
