OL,3,CTrump files lawsuit against the BBC
OL,4,Cover Panorama speech edit
OL,6,FThe fallout from the report also led
OL,7,Fto the resignation of both the
OL,8,Fdirector-general Tim Davie and the
OL,9,Fhead of news Deborah Turness.
OL,11,FDespite the apology, Mr Trump said he
OL,12,Fwould proceed with legal action for
OL,13,F"anywhere between one billion dollars
OL,14,F(#759.8 million) and five billion
OL,15,Fdollars (#3.79 billion)".
OL,17,FMr Trump has a history of suing news
OL,18,Forganisations in the US and is engaged
OL,19,Fin legal action with the New York
OL,20,FTimes and the Wall Street Journal.
