OL,6,FBBC News reported that the broadcaster
OL,7,Fhad set out five main arguments in a
OL,8,Fletter to Mr Trump's legal team as to
OL,9,Fwhy it did not believe there was a
OL,10,Fbasis for a defamation claim.
OL,12,FThe BBC has been contacted for comment.
